{"tid":1470320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆搵仔: 學下接納唔同人嘅意見","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:03:57.000Z","uid":29625,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3041def412f12e8965320ceaa04ae08249aad6dc","tid":1470320,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:54:43.000Z","msg":"做得唔啱要檢討同埋改善<br />\n做人要be humble<br />\n人哋善意批評要聽<br />\n核彈都唔撚割唔係俾你揸正牌去做乜撚嘢都得<br />\n咪撚再喺度人哋同你唔同意見就鬧人分化割𥱊<br />\n一尾堅持幾件乜撚嘢都唔聽走去抹黑人<br />\n咁樣做同個仆街支共政府有咩分別？<br />\n所以唔該<br />\n全部人都要be humble<br />\n學下接納唔同人嘅意見<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%A0%B8%E5%BD%88%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E5%89%B2-%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%94%BE%E6%A0%B8%E5%BD%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%25BD%2588%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2589%25B2-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%25BD%2588%2F&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w6npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=09aeefcb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%25BD%2588%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2589%25B2-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%25BD%2588%2F&h=66c419ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%A0%B8%E5%BD%88%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E5%89%B2-%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%94%BE%E6%A0%B8%E5%BD%88/</a>"},{"pid":"e534920b48e0a041c188b69f41bcb6724ff2cf19","tid":1470320,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:10.000Z","msg":"陳雲：<br />\n做錯事不道歉，是違反道德的啊。這個當然，但我們不是在小學課室，由班長和班主任裁判，我們是在戰場上，警察、法官、電視台、報紙、觀眾都是中共的人。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你道歉，對方就有材料展開政治謠言宣傳，而且要求你再為其他你無做過的事道歉（例如毆打北京記者），之後你拒絕，他們就向你開火射擊。</span></span>做錯了事就馬上走，不是道歉！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">普選勝利了，在民選元首認為安全的情況</span></span>，才為以往的錯失道歉，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">道歉也是元首來做，不是民眾來做</span></span>，賠償也是用政府的錢，不是民間眾籌。"},{"pid":"bfe902f0a389e84b4fc8e7cb7cb9a882b63e0355","tid":1470320,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/henGSOg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhenGSOg.png&h=334dafd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b01a088a87d07b71789fb970738cbd52247e42ac","tid":1470320,"uid":29625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:56:57.000Z","msg":"老豆搵仔都出埋post提醒大家不割蓆=/=不檢討不接受意見<br />\n連登仔可唔可以冷靜啲唔好再信啲三毛煽動分化<br />\n三毛唔止扮和理非非批評，仲會扮硬頸勇武發爛渣架<br />\n你洗版式咁反駁只係火上加油架咋"},{"pid":"bcc30d055fbc2e9067a6ef29914c9d236c398173","tid":1470320,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n818 止黑暴，制警亂 大遊行<br />\n<br />\n爆眼 插竹 腦出血"}]}